{"title":"那一场雨","authors":["王怀让"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":5,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一场雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王怀让"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着三千六百五十张日历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我依然能够看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一场雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一场在十二月落下的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淅淅沥沥的春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那场雨一直下到现在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐浴在那场雨里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宛若读一首诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当初像读一首朦胧诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似懂非懂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今像哼一支流行曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很上口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在雨中行进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请不要打伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论多漂亮的伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会挡住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对诗意的体验"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}